properties.name: 2025 Los Angeles Marathon
properties.desc: The 2025 Los Angeles Marathon presented by ASICS takes you on a thrilling journey through the heart of the city. Starting at Dodger Stadium, this 26.2-mile course showcases LA’s diverse neighborhoods and iconic landmarks. You’ll pass by Chinatown, the Hollywood Walk of Fame, Sunset Boulevard, Rodeo Drive in Beverly Hills, and the vibrant streets of Westwood before finishing at the scenic Avenue of the Stars in Century City. Whether you’re chasing a personal best or soaking in the sights, this course promises a unique and unforgettable race experience!
